I tighten the tie around my neck

Weapons Storage reports that we are almost out of gunpowder.
We need to replenish our supplies before the next battle.
We have got new recruits too, so we probably need new weapons too.
Let us make today's mission a descent to Guild.
I am kind of not good with heights...
We are not descending from the sky, we are going down underground.
It is a place deep underground that we call Guild.
Our comrades are making weapons there.
It is there so that Angel does not find out about it?
If she took down Guild, we would lose our source of ammunition and any chances of winning.
We will be headed your way tonight.
We will leave deactivating the traps to you.
We will be going with everyone present here.
Is it okay to leave Noda behind?
That idiot's probably just doing whatever he wants again.
Come on do not stand around, we are going.
It is been a while since I have been to Guild.
Otonashi, I do not recognize you as one of us yet.
Why on earth did he go out of his way to wait here for us?
Noda - kun likes to stress the importance of the moment.
I do not particularly want to be accepted by you.
The traps have not been deactivated?!
It is exactly as you can see.
The route to Guild has several anti - Angel instant - fatality traps set up.
This means that they are all still active.
Maybe they forgot to deactivate them?
Are they trying to wipe us out?
No, Guild used their own judgment and reset the traps.
There could only be one reason.
The guys at Guild would do this even though they know we are on the way?
It seems you do not understand yet.
Whatever happens, it is not like we will die.
Although, we will experience the pain of it...
That is the part I do not like...
But if Guild's whereabouts are discovered and they fall, we will no longer be able to replenish ammo or replace broken weapons.
How would we be able to fight Angel in that state?
While the traps are still set?
Angel will be taken down by the traps right?
The traps will only slow her down.
By the way, what kind of traps are there?
Everyone else seems to be okay.
Was it okay not to rescue him?
It is not like he will die.
If we leave him alone he will find his way above ground on his own.
It is fine, I quite like you.
This is a trap that shuts you in!
Do not forget something so important!!
What happens if you touch that?
It will cut your body clean in half.
What was the third beam again?
How are we supposed to avoid that?
Everyone, just do what you can!
You do not want to see that.
The victim this time was Matsushita - kun, huh.
There was no helping it with his build.
That guy needs to go on a diet.
That must have been a pretty terrible sight.
Right in front of him, too.
I am glad you made it through.
Incidentally, even if you get cut into pieces, you will return to normal after a while.
The ceiling comes down in here!
I said do not forget things like that!
Run to her and hug her tight!
Like I said, it is all good.
Do not let his sacrifice go to waste, let us go.
You are too heavy, I cannot hold on!
Should Otonashi and I drop down?
Wait a second, do not decide things on your own!
It would not be good to lose our forces all at once here.
I get it, hurry and climb up!
I do not really have a choice, right?
You are quite a sadist, are not you.
Why does she smell so good?
Why are you facing this way?
W - Will you hurry up and climb?
Do not hold yourself up using that!!
You did well to survive, newbie.
The next one will be you.
That puppy's going to be washed away!
Even Shiina - san fell prey to a trap!
Or rather, you can tell just by looking at it...
Her weakness is her love for cute things.
That is actually pretty cute of her.
But she will be okay, right?
Looks like you are the only one left.
If this were a real army, everyone would be dead.
They would be useless if they were not this effective.
Why do not we take a break?
I want to dry off these clothes.
It is amazing how you can command those crazy guys.
Why did you get chosen as the leader?
Because I was the first to rebel.
Unlike you, I kept my memories.
When you were alive, before you came to this world?
I was the eldest, with two younger sisters and a brother.
My parents did well in their jobs, so we were a really wealthy family.
Our house was surrounded by nature.
It was almost like a holiday home.
Our parents were out that afternoon.
Some men we did not know came into the house.
They were wearing balaclavas even though it was the middle of summer.
You could immediately tell that they were up to no good.
I thought that as the eldest, I had to protect my siblings.
But there was no way I could, right?
They were after money, of course.
But they could not find anything.
They ran around smashing windows and TVs, and started to get angry.
Then they thought up the worst possible thing for us.
Little girl, you are the eldest.
They must have told you where the valuables are.
If there is an earthquake, take it and run, or, If a burglar comes, give it to them and tell them to go away.
They must have told you something.
They did not tell me anything like that!
Come now, why do not you go search for something?
If we do not like it, you might have to say goodbye to one of these kids here.
Come back with one in ten minutes.
My head was in so much pain.
I was nauseous and about to collapse.
But their lives were on the line.
But I did not know of anything valuable.
If I bring this big vase...
If it is this heavy, it has to be really valuable!
The police came thirty minutes later.
I was the only one left.
I do not really care if I become a water flea or whatever.
All I want to do is fight God if he really does exist.
We had not done anything wrong.
Yet on that day, even with my confidence as an older sister,
everything I wanted to protect was stolen from me within the space of 30 minutes.
How could it be that unreasonable?
I cannot accept that kind of life.
You are strong are not you, Yuri?
If I had memories like that, I think I would want to vanish as soon as possible.
Can I ask you one thing?
I did not commit suicide or anything.
Why would someone who committed suicide bother fighting?
And anyway, there is no one in this world who died by suicide.
I am going to protect you.
You managed to fight your way through all those traps!
Never mind that, where is Angel?
She stopped for a while, but she is on the move again.
Yeah, we cannot just stop making weapons!
What is important is not locations or weapons.
In this world, nothing that has life can be created.
However, things that just have form can be.
If you have the method and means to make something, there is no problem creating it.
You can even create it out of dirt.
However, efficiency became prioritized and now all we do is make replicas in this factory.
Is this guy in high school too?
Basically, we just breathe life into something that looks like what we remember.
We will head for Old Guild then.
It is a place we abandoned long ago.
There is nothing left there, but there are mountains of dirt.
We can get up to ground level from there too.
We will not hand over Old Guild to Angel.
That is the sole remaining place for us.
Your only necessary belongings are your memories and your pride as a craftsman.
There are no more traps left.
There is nothing for me to do down there anyway.
She can hold her own in close combat?
Can we really do that here?
It is fine, just do it!
Looks like you guys can pull through if you try!
That does not look like it was easy to make.
I guess we cannot just put together stuff we do not know remember...
Do not just put random things together!!
I wonder how many years its been...
You will get as much dirt as you want if you poke around the walls.
This is one run down joint.
We are counting on you again.
Alright, let us get to work!
We blew up Guild, and Angel with it.
We will replenish supplies as quickly as possible.
Head to Old Guild before Angel recovers.
I repeat, hurry up you idiots.
All I want to do is fight God if he really does exist.
You could not sing the song you like.
I see you in a different light.
